data.description: Contract Pending  Welcome to this cute 1.5 story home that has so much potential! The home boats over 1200 square feet of opportunity at an affordable price! Some great value added updates include a brand new HVAC system in 2023, and a newer roof as well as siding. The main floor consists of a spacious living room, an easy access main floor laundry, with a nice sized kitchen! Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms with a full bathroom! With a fully fenced in yard and off street parking, this little gem is a fantastic opportunity to get into an affordable home, with so much potential!
